    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Two tapping scripts for Day 10 of the sleep arc. The first works with the fragility of new calm — the part that expects stress to return. The second releases the adrenaline that the body accumulates across a busy day, so it can fully stop."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "New to tapping? Read "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"}}],
            "text": "how EFT tapping works"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " first."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The practice"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Script 1: Stabilise your gains"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Karate chop"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though calm still feels new and a little fragile, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though part of me expects the stress to return, I honour my progress over these days."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though peace can feel temporary, I'm open to making it my baseline."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tapping round"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I've felt real changes — small, steady, noticeable."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My body remembers how to soften sooner."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My mind recognises when it's spinning."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Old habits still knock, but I don't have to let them in."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Calm is becoming familiar instead of foreign."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm less reactive and more responsive."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can feel a new rhythm forming."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " This is the life I'm building, one calm choice at a time."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I trust this new calm taking root in me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My nervous system is relearning safety and stability."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Peace fits me better every day."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I strengthen it with every breath and boundary."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Calm is a practice I own."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I anchor this as my new normal."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My body, mind, and emotions align around rest."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " This foundation carries me into easy sleep."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Script 2: Release adrenaline and busyness"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Karate chop"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I've spent the whole day running on adrenaline, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I've been in motion from the moment I woke up, I honour that I've done my best."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though my body still feels like it needs to keep going, I'm open to letting it power down now."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tapping round"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My body's been running on overdrive all day."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can feel the buzz still moving through me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " It's hard to slow down when I've lived in fast-forward for so long."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My brain still thinks it needs to do something."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " But right now, nothing needs to be done."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " The work is finished; the world can wait."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I've earned the right to stop."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My body can finally shift from doing to being."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I give my body permission to unwind."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " The adrenaline can drain away safely now."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My muscles relax as I settle into calm."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I trust that rest restores everything effort cannot."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm safe to stop completely."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My breath gets deeper, slower, softer."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My body is learning peace again."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I drift into sleep with ease, grounded and free."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times."}]
      },
